Aquaman Actress  Amber  Heard Secretly Welcomes Baby Girl Oonagh Paige born via surrogate]#Shorts

Miss Heard  took to her  Instagram  page on Thursday  to reveal  to the  world  some  exciting personal  milestone.

''The birth of  her baby  daughter Oonagh  Paige Heard''. 


According  To  page six and miss Heard ,  Baby Oonagh   was  born on  the 8th of  April  This  year  via a surrogate  and  The   actress  is "proud"  to  be  the  listed  sole  legal parent.


In  the  post  Page six,  also  stated that  Baby  Oonagh's middle  name,  Paige,  is inspired by  the  actress's late  mother  who passed  away  in 2020.


In her  Instagram post  miss   Heard post "I'm so  excited  to share  this  news with  you .Four years ago,  I decided  I wanted  to  have  a child. I wanted  to  it on my own  terms. I now  appreciate how  radical   is for  us as women to think  about  one  of the  most fundamental parts  of  our destinies  in this way .I we  hope    arrive  at  a point  which  it's normalized to not want a ring in order to have a crib. A  part of me wants to uphold that my private life is none of anyone's business .
I also get that the nature of my job compels me to take control of this .My daughter was born on  April 8th, 2021.
Her  name  is Oonagh  Paige  Heard .She's the  beginning  of the rest of  my  life".


Miss heard is set to return as Mera in  Aquman  and the lost kingdom, a highly anticipated sequel film which began production recently.

The film will star Jason Momoa, Yahya Abdul -Mateen 2nd, Patrick Wilson,  A new face Pilou Asbaek and will be directed by James Wan.
